# Search with ripgrep

Use `rg` (ripgrep) for text searches instead of `grep`. Fall back to `grep` only when `rg` is not installed.

- Prefer: `rg pattern`, `rg -n 'foo' src/`
- Check availability: `command -v rg >/dev/null 2>&1 && rg pattern || grep -rn pattern .`
